{"tid":1271104,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警黑再度合作，今晚留守的兄弟be water","createTime":"2019-07-01T05:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T05:31:51.000Z","uid":265332,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d7636617de88fa442360bae23f61575d949962b","tid":1271104,"uid":265332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:14:52.000Z","msg":"各位：<br />\n<br />\n今日萬事小心，林鄭已失勢，西環宜家發功，開大水喉，警黑再度合作，琴日的撐警大會已露出端倪：<br />\n<br />\n1)何君堯琴日個萬人造勢大會，黑社會再度撑場：<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190630/59774407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F59774407&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgfsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=bec00ab5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F59774407&h=4734c760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190630/59774407</a><br />\n<br />\n2)認識一名住精神病復康院舍的親友收到短訊，去撑警會收$1,800,集合時收$900,散場收$900，證明背後有人泵水<br />\n<br />\n3)有雙氧水混入生理盬水混入救傷站到，大家小心<br />\n<br />\n警察被人鬧，咁就惟有黑社會出手，呢種玩法，係佔中時已用過，所以今晚打算遊行完留守的兄弟，Be water，不受傷不流血不被捕<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I think the best way is when the police are all equipped and ready to storm out, we leave all of sudden and let them watch.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n切切為你們祈禱<br />\n<br />\n一個耶膠上"},{"pid":"4bac3e271d11e678cf30ddca9e36586337de8018","tid":1271104,"uid":168675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:18:40.000Z","msg":"小心"},{"pid":"2a48579e81776e7415a7dbd4587423e8699ca526","tid":1271104,"uid":64956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"幫推"}]}